content.description: Sit start in the mid-right of the block to the right of the small tree. hands on the low, good finger edge. Dyno directly to the top. top out
content.location: Sit start in the mid-right of the block to the right of the small tree.

content.description: Sit start on the mid-right of the block, just to the right of the small tree.   Sit start on the good edge and move up through slots to attain the good top out directly above.
content.location: Sit start on the mid-right of the block, just to the right of the tree.

content.description: Sit start in the middle of the boulder on a good ledge, and with the first feet you can acquire in the middle of the block...   Traverse left along the low, diminishing seam. stop halfway across seam and go up with quartzite crystal pebbles and small edges to the top... use heel hooks...
content.location: Sit start in the middle of the boulder on a good ledge, and with the first feet you can acquire in the middle of the block...

content.description:
A small block with a few short problems. This is probably not worth your time, but it is here and just minutes from the parking area. 

  I honestly wouldn't bother climbing here unless you have done everything else.
